message: Why worry about things you cannot control when you can keep yourself busy controlling the things that depend on you?
title: Thought of the day

author: Laozi
message: When you are content to be simply yourself and don't compare or compete, everybody will respect you.
title: Thought of the day

author: William Shakespeare
message: Be not afraid of greatness: some are born great, some achieve greatness, and some have greatness thrust upon them.
title: Thought of the day

author: George Sheehan
message: Success means having the courage, the determination, and the will to become the person you believe you were meant to be.
title: Thought of the day
